name: NewYorkJazzBars
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new york bars
des:
Selecting an area, a list of jazz bars in that area is shown. 
If you select a number, the address of the bar will be shown. 
Devices with a screen can display a map.
To search bars in another area, say reset and then select the area.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
